---
import Layout from '../../components/layout/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_NAME, SITE_URL } from '../../config';
import { buildBreadcrumbSchema } from '../../lib/seo';

const title = 'Legal Notice - Website Terms and Legal Information';
const description = 'Legal notice with publisher information, hosting, intellectual property, privacy policy, GDPR rights, terms of use, liability limitations and governing law for Spanish salary calculators.';

const schemas = [
  buildBreadcrumbSchema([
    { name: 'Home', url: '/en/' },
    { name: 'Legal Notice', url: '/en/legal-notice/' },
  ]),
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} schema={schemas} locale="en">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-8">
    <nav class="mb-6 text-sm text-medium-gray">
      <a href="/en/" class="hover:text-brand">Home</a> / <span class="text-charcoal dark:text-gray-200">Legal Notice</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">Legal Notice</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-dark-gray dark:text-gray-300 space-y-6">
      <p><em>Last updated: June {new Date().getFullYear()}</em></p>

      <p>
        In accordance with applicable consumer protection and digital services legislation, the following
        legal notice is provided to users and visitors of the website {SITE_URL}. By accessing and browsing
        this website, users acknowledge and accept these terms in their entirety.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">1. Website Identification</h2>
      <p>
        In compliance with the duty of information set forth in Article 10 of Law 34/2002 on Information
        Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE), the following details are provided:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Publisher:</strong> Mottalib Radif</li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href={SITE_URL} class="text-brand hover:underline">{SITE_URL}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Brand name:</strong> {SITE_NAME}</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@elsueldoneto.es" class="text-brand hover:underline">contact@elsueldoneto.es</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        The publisher assumes editorial responsibility for all content published on the website, with the
        exception of results generated by the salary calculators, which depend on data entered by the user
        and on the tax and social security parameters in effect at the date of consultation.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">2. Hosting</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted by:<br>
        <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — GitHub, Inc.<br>
        88 Colin P Kelly Jr Street, San Francisco, CA 94107, United States<br>
        Website: <a href="https://pages.github.com" class="text-brand hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://pages.github.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        GitHub Pages is a static website hosting service provided by GitHub, Inc., a subsidiary of Microsoft
        Corporation. The infrastructure relies on a global content delivery network (CDN) that serves pages
        from the server closest to each visitor. HTTPS is used to encrypt all data in transit. As a technical
        host, GitHub, Inc. does not exercise any editorial control over the website's content.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">3. About This Website</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>{SITE_NAME}</strong> is an independent information platform offering free salary calculators
        and financial tools for Spain. All calculations are performed locally in your browser using
        client-side JavaScript; no personal data is sent to our servers. The website provides informational
        content about salary, taxes, social security contributions and other fiscal concepts in Spain.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All content on this website, including but not limited to text, graphics, images, logos, icons,
        software, source code, calculation algorithms, page layouts and design elements, is the property of
        Mottalib Radif or its licensors and is protected by Spanish and international intellectual property
        laws.
      </p>
      <p>
        Reproduction, distribution, public communication, transformation, reverse engineering, or any form
        of commercial use without express written authorization is strictly prohibited. Users are authorised
        to browse the website for strictly personal and private use. Brief quotations for informational
        purposes are permitted provided the source is credited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">5. Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} respects your privacy and is committed to protecting personal data in compliance with the
        General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR — Regulation EU 2016/679) and the Spanish Organic Law 3/2018
        on Personal Data Protection and Digital Rights (LOPDGDD). All salary calculations are performed
        entirely in your web browser. No personal data is transmitted to our servers. See our full
        <a href="/en/privacy-policy/" class="text-brand hover:underline">privacy policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">6. Cookie Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses <strong>no tracking cookies</strong>. No advertising, profiling, or third-party
        cookies are placed. User preferences are stored in the browser's localStorage, which is not a cookie
        and is never transmitted to our servers. See our full
        <a href="/en/cookie-policy/" class="text-brand hover:underline">cookie policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">7. Data Protection (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with Articles 15 to 22 of the GDPR and the LOPDGDD, every user has the following
        rights:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Right of access</strong> (Art. 15): obtain confirmation of whether personal data is being processed.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> (Art. 16): obtain correction of inaccurate data.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> (Art. 17): obtain deletion of personal data.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to restriction</strong> (Art. 18): restrict processing in certain cases.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to portability</strong> (Art. 20): receive data in a machine-readable format.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to object</strong> (Art. 21): object to processing on grounds relating to your situation.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to withdraw consent</strong> (Art. 7): withdraw consent at any time.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Since the website does not collect personal data, these rights are currently not applicable in
        practice. For any enquiry, contact us at contact@elsueldoneto.es. We undertake to respond within
        30 days. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD):
        <a href="https://www.aepd.es" class="text-brand hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aepd.es</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">8. Terms of Use</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing {SITE_URL}, you agree to these terms. The website is accessible free of charge. The
        publisher uses all reasonable means to ensure quality access but is under no obligation of result.
        Access may be interrupted at any time for maintenance or updates. Users agree to use the website in
        accordance with its intended purpose and not for unlawful purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} provides financial calculation tools and informational content for educational purposes
        only. The calculations and information provided do not constitute professional tax, legal, or
        financial advice. While we strive for accuracy based on current Spanish legislation, we cannot
        guarantee that results are error-free or reflect the latest regulatory changes. Users should verify
        calculations with qualified tax advisors or official sources such as the Agencia Tributaria (AEAT).
      </p>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} shall not be held liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or
        punitive damages arising from the use of or inability to use this website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">10. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to third-party websites, including official government sites
        (agenciatributaria.es, seg-social.es). {SITE_NAME} is not responsible for the content, privacy
        practices, or availability of these external sites. The inclusion of any link does not imply
        endorsement of the linked website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">11. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        This legal notice is governed by Spanish law. Any disputes arising from the use of this website
        shall be submitted to the courts and tribunals of the domicile of the user, in accordance with
        applicable consumer protection legislation. The potential invalidity of any clause shall not
        affect the remaining provisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">12. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>
        The European Commission provides an online dispute resolution (ODR) platform:
        <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" class="text-brand hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.
        We are not obliged and not willing to participate in a dispute resolution procedure before a
        consumer arbitration board.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">13. Changes and Contact</h2>
      <p>
        The publisher reserves the right to modify this legal notice at any time. Changes take effect upon
        publication. For questions, contact us at:<br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:contact@elsueldoneto.es" class="text-brand hover:underline">contact@elsueldoneto.es</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
